512
00:22:17,475 --> 00:22:19,274
I'm not stopping.

513
00:22:19,275 --> 00:22:22,675
Beside, remember what Gramps Jirokichi was bragging about?

514
00:22:23,975 --> 00:22:28,175
This motorbike is rigged with an acceleration function.

515
00:22:30,175 --> 00:22:32,074
See you, great detective.

516
00:22:32,075 --> 00:22:34,274
I'll leave that treasure to you.

517
00:22:34,275 --> 00:22:37,274
I wasn't after that treasure, to begin with.

518
00:22:37,275 --> 00:22:40,575
Besides, all I did was take him on because he challenged me.

519
00:23:17,175 --> 00:23:18,575
That punk.

520
00:23:52,975 --> 00:23:54,974
You've got no dream.

521
00:23:54,975 --> 00:23:57,175
Idiot. Of course, I do.

522
00:24:00,275 --> 00:24:03,875
