524
00:24:11,575 --> 00:24:13,174
Right.

525
00:24:13,175 --> 00:24:16,474
Why? Conan's the one who protected the treasure, right?

526
00:24:16,475 --> 00:24:18,274
So, this is why.

527
00:24:18,275 --> 00:24:22,475
That brat. How dare he take away the headlines from me.

528
00:24:26,075 --> 00:24:30,074
"Next Episode" -If I keep believing, he'll come back.

529
00:24:30,075 --> 00:24:32,574
It can't be. There's something wrong.

530
00:24:32,575 --> 00:24:34,674
It's impossible for her lover

531
00:24:34,675 --> 00:24:35,675
